# Egress allowlist for the agent-runner (POSIX extended regex, one host pattern per line,
# matched case-insensitively against the destination host). DENY-BY-DEFAULT is set in
# tinyproxy.conf (FilterDefaultDeny Yes) — only hosts matching a line here are reachable.
#
# The `(^|\.)host$` form matches the apex AND its subdomains, but NOT a look-alike that
# merely ends with the string (e.g. `evilgithub.com` does NOT match `(^|\.)github\.com$`).
# Keep this list MINIMAL — every entry widens what a prompt-injected agent could reach.

# Anthropic — the Claude Code CLI (the agent model API).
(^|\.)anthropic\.com$

# GitHub — git clone/fetch/push over HTTPS, the REST API (gh), and raw/asset content.
(^|\.)github\.com$
(^|\.)githubusercontent\.com$
